These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, d&b
1. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the fan of punk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Job           | social-worker | teacher |
| Music-Genre   | d&b     | punk  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
2 different pets are kept: hamster, horse
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, helicopter
1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the owner of the hamster##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Pet         | horse   | hamster      |
| Transport   | bus | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, metal
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, helicopter
1. the fan of d&b is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| Music-Genre   | metal | d&b    |
| Transport     | jet-ski | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-4::.
